ActsAsHuman
===========

Adds:
  full_name
and
  full_name=
instance methods to a model

Adds validations to ensure that the names are reasonable.

Requires:
  first_name, last_name and middle_names fields on the model

Example
=======

class User < ActiveRecord::Base
  acts_as_human
end

